@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}


<div class="hero hero-2" style="background-image: url('../../images/background1.jpg');">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-center mx-auto">
                <div class="intro">

                    <h1 class="heading mb-2" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">About Us</h1>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <p class="text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">

                        Our team’s name is The Cyco Paths, being a homophone take on the word psychopath, it does not mean that we all have a personality disorder; but rather we are trying to adapt the traits of charisma, fearlessness, smart and determination of a psychopath. Cyco can have a lot of meanings including cycle, cyber, cycling and psychology as demonstrated by our icon, the word path also has a connotation of one's course through life, their purpose, and final destination. In essence, our overall vision is to be fearless in our actions and to combine fitness with technology to provide the public with innovative solutions.

                        Our team consists of a group of intelligent Monash students from different fields of study (including IT, DS, BIS). We will be working as a team and bridging our skill gaps to develop IT products that are contributed to social good

                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="contact-info">

                    <div class="address mt-4">
                        <i class="icon-room"></i>
                        <h4 class="mb-2">Location:</h4>
                        <p>Monash University, Wellington Road, Clayton, VIC, 3800, AU</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="open-hours mt-4">
                        <i class="icon-clock-o"></i>
                        <h4 class="mb-2">Open Hours:</h4>
                        <p>
                            Sunday-Friday:<br>
                            11:00 AM - 2300 PM
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="email mt-4">
                        <i class="icon-envelope"></i>
                        <h4 class="mb-2">Email:</h4>
                        <p>info@Colorlib</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="phone mt-4">
                        <i class="icon-phone"></i>
                        <h4 class="mb-2">Call:</h4>
                        <p>+61 3 9902 6000</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <form action="#">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-6 mb-3">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Name">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 mb-3">
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Email">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 mb-3">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Subject">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 mb-3">
                            <textarea name="" id="" cols="30" rows="7" class="form-control" placeholder="Message"></textarea>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12">
                            <input type="submit" value="Leave Us A Message" class="btn btn-primary">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> <!-- /.untree_co-section -->